column2: "... Oh, I haven't seen you in a while, but you seem to be doing well."
"I'm aware of what you're capable of, but try not to over extend yourself."
"If we were to lose you, it could cause a lot of problems."
"Me? I got tired of bullying Zeno-boy, so I'm out on patrol."
"I don't know why, but it seems the Darkers have been really active in this area."
"Because of that, the guard robots have been more active as well. Makes things all the more hectic."
"Also, I've heard rumors of a new type of Darker appearing around here. So take care of yourself."
